    public class EnumInput<E extends java.lang.Enum<E>>
extends TextInput
implements ListInput<java.lang.String,E>, OptionalListInput<java.lang.String,E>, PreSelectInput<java.lang.String,E>
    Input to select values from a Java Enum the DB will contain the Enum name and the menu the result of the toString call.
